<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home | Logistics Company</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2c3e50;
            --secondary: #3498db;
            --accent: #e74c3c;
            --light: #ecf0f1;
            --dark: #2c3e50;
            --gray: #7f8c8d;
            --border-radius: 8px;
            --box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

				.user-info {
					display: flex;
					align-items: center;
					gap: 10px;
					margin-bottom: 1rem;
				}

				.client-name {
					margin-left: 8px;
					color: white;
				}

				.user-info i {
					margin-top: 50%;
					color: white;
				}

				.logout-link {
					margin-left: 10px;
					color: red;
					text-decoration: none;
				} 

				.bg-dark {
					background-color: rgb(1 1 1) !important;
				}

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }
        
        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.8), rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.9)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504805572947-34fad45aed93?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 120px 0 80px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--secondary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .btn-outline-light {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid white;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-outline-light:hover {
            background: white;
            color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .btn i {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Features Section */
        .features {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        
        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 60px;
        }
        
        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .section-header h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--secondary);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .section-header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--gray);
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            height: 100%;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
        }
        
        .feature-icon i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }
        
        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--gray);
        }
        
        /* Tracking Section */
        .tracking {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), #1a2530);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        
        .tracking-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 50px;
        }
        
        .tracking-content {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }
        
        .tracking-form {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        }
        
        .tracking-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .tracking-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .tracking-form h3 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--secondary);
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.2);
        }
        
        .btn-block {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        /* Services Section */
        .services {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: var(--light);
        }
        
        .service-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            transition: var(--transition);
            height: 100%;
        }
        
        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .service-img {
            height: 200px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .service-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .service-card:hover .service-img img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        
        .service-content {
            padding: 25px;
        }
        
        .service-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .service-content p {
            color: var(--gray);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .service-content a {
            color: var(--secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 60;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .service-content a i {
            margin-left: 5px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        
        .service-content a:hover i {
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }
        
        /* Testimonials */
        .testimonials {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        
        .testimonial-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            padding: 30px;
            position: relative;
            margin: 30px 15px;
        }
        
        .testimonial-card::before {
            content: '"';
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1);
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .testimonial-content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .testimonial-author {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .author-img {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        
        .author-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        .author-info h4 {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .author-info p {
            color: var(--gray);
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 80px 0 50px;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .section-header h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- DEBUG -->
    <!-- Navbar (You'll need to include your actual navbar partial) -->

		<%- include('./partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Deliver with Confidence, Receive with Ease</h1>
            <p>Fast, reliable, and secure logistics solutions for all your shipping needs. Wherever you need it, whenever you need it.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/clients/send-package" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-box me-2"></i> Send a Package
                    </a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-2"></i> Get Started
                    </a>
                <% } %>
                <a href="/tracking" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                    <i class="fas fa-search me-2"></i> Track a Shipment
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
                <p>We provide logistics solutions that ensure your packages are delivered safely and on time</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Fast Delivery</h3>
                        <p>Express shipping options with guaranteed delivery times for urgent shipments.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Secure Handling</h3>
                        <p>Advanced security measures to ensure your packages arrive safely and intact.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Global Reach</h3>
                        <p>International shipping to over 200 countries with customs clearance support.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>24/7 Support</h3>
                        <p>Our customer service team is available around the clock to assist you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Competitive Pricing</h3>
                        <p>Affordable rates without compromising on service quality or reliability.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-route"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Real-Time Tracking</h3>
                        <p>Monitor your shipment's journey from pickup to delivery with live updates.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Tracking Section -->
    <section class="tracking">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="tracking-container">
                <div class="tracking-content">
                    <h2>Track Your Shipment</h2>
                    <p>Enter your tracking number to get real-time updates on your package's location and estimated delivery time.</p>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i> Learn More About Services
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tracking-form">
                    <h3>Track Package</h3>
                    <form>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter Tracking Number" required>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                            <i class="fas fa-search me-2"></i> Track Now
                        </button>
                    </form>
                    <div class="mt-3 text-center">
                        <a href="/help" class="text-muted">Need help finding your tracking number?</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Our Services</h2>
                <p>Comprehensive logistics solutions tailored to your specific needs</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <div class="service-img">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566576721346-d4a3b4eaeb55?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Domestic Shipping">
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-content">
                            <h3>Domestic Shipping</h3>
                            <p>Fast and reliable delivery services within the country with next-day options available.</p>
                            <a href="/services/domestic">
                                Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <div class="service-img">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533750349088-cd871a92f312?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="International Shipping">
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-content">
                            <h3>International Shipping</h3>
                            <p>Global delivery solutions with customs clearance and package consolidation.</p>
                            <a href="/services/international">
                                Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <div class="service-img">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560448204-e02f11c3d0e2?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Freight Services">
                        </div>
                        <div class="service-content">
                            <h3>Freight Services</h3>
                            <p>Heavy cargo and pallet shipments with specialized handling and transportation.</p>
                            <a href="/services/freight">
                                Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>What Our Customers Say</h2>
                <p>Trusted by businesses and individuals worldwide</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>Their international shipping service saved our business when we had urgent documents to deliver. Fast and reliable!</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <div class="author-img">
                                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/32.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson">
                            </div>
                            <div class="author-info">
                                <h4>Sarah Johnson</h4>
                                <p>Small Business Owner</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>The real-time tracking feature gives me peace of mind knowing exactly where my packages are at all times.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <div class="author-img">
                                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/54.jpg" alt="Michael Chen">
                            </div>
                            <div class="author-info">
                                <h4>Michael Chen</h4>
                                <p>E-commerce Seller</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="testimonial-card">
                        <div class="testimonial-content">
                            <p>Their customer support team went above and beyond to resolve a customs issue for us. Highly recommended!</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="testimonial-author">
                            <div class="author-img">
                                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/68.jpg" alt="Emma Rodriguez">
                            </div>
                            <div class="author-info">
                                <h4>Emma Rodriguez</h4>
                                <p>Import/Export Manager</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer (You'll need to include your actual footer partial) -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
